QuestData.Title: Nav Test: Zereth Mortis
QuestData.Description:
This quest will take you through a likely flow for the 9.2 Main Line questing. We don't have a finalized pitch for the 9.2 Main Line yet, so this is just a rough idea of how the POIs might be used.
This test is built to be Beastmaster and Godmode friendly, so feel free to use cheats.
Useful cheats: 92BrokerTown - Return to hub 92NavTest - Restart the Nav Test (Must abandon first)

Objectives.Objective: Return to Broker Town (End of Chapter) (Cheat: 92BrokerTown)
Return to Broker Town (End of Chapter) (Cheat: 92BrokerTown)
Broker Camp: Secondary Hub (Free flight path)
